Alternatively get yourself a Larrikan's mask from Sebilis, a rather common drop and they sell for around 200pp (last time I saw one) on Tarew Marr. These have 10 casts of improved invisibility, with a normal cast time. &quot;More expensive than 10 invis potions!&quot; I hear you cry. Use this until expended and buy another mask with another character (they are lore). Now sell the full mask to a vendor for about 1gp, then sell the empty mask to the vendor. Now buy both masks back for about 8gp each, they will both be fully charged. 10 charges of invis for less than 1pp per time in one slot, and less hassle and cheaper than a gnomish vanishing device.<br>
<br>
You can also use this to charge many devices, with varying levels of expense, ie a locket of escape is 250pp buy back.<br>
<br>
I would recommend carrying a normal invis potion as a back up (insta invis is great, especially when getting up from FD in the middle of a group of mobs).<br>
<br>
Enjoy. <p>Talonite <BR>
